        Buying and Selling Simultaneously in Queensland: How Simultaneous Settlements Work
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A simultaneous settlement lets you sell your existing home and settle your new purchase on the same day. It is possible and common, but it requires careful planning from both your agent and your solicitor.
      </p>
    </div>
